277
00:22:00,818 --> 00:22:01,828
Enjoy.

278
00:22:12,838 --> 00:22:14,338
Have some kimchi.

279
00:22:19,888 --> 00:22:20,798
Water?

280
00:22:24,928 --> 00:22:26,138
Here you go.

281
00:22:30,058 --> 00:22:30,938
Are you okay?

282
00:22:38,318 --> 00:22:40,528
Sir, they're so romantic.

283
00:22:40,608 --> 00:22:41,618
Shush.

284
00:22:43,738 --> 00:22:46,118
This is what a real fiancée is like.

285
00:22:46,698 --> 00:22:50,618
First, you have to show people
how sincere and devoted you are.

286
00:22:51,628 --> 00:22:53,918
You touch their hearts like that first.

287
00:22:54,628 --> 00:22:55,998
Then I get revenge step by step.

288
00:22:56,088 --> 00:22:57,128
That's right.

289
00:23:13,978 --> 00:23:14,938
Drink this.

290
00:23:15,018 --> 00:23:17,278
