00:40:46,818 --> 00:40:49,618
You need to bring up memories
that the patient is familiar with.

542
00:40:49,698 --> 00:40:52,578
For example, you can stimulate
his brain with special memories

543
00:40:52,748 --> 00:40:56,538
such as memorable places
or his favorite foods.

544
00:40:56,628 --> 00:41:00,168
It'll require significant efforts
from his guardian.

545
00:41:00,748 --> 00:41:01,758
Understood, sir.

546
00:41:01,878 --> 00:41:05,468
Then please tell me everything
that the guardian needs to do.

547
00:41:05,548 --> 00:41:08,678
But his guardian is doing
such a great job already.

548
00:41:08,758 --> 00:41:10,388
His guardian?

549
00:41:11,058 --> 00:41:12,728
Who would that be?

550
00:41:12,808 --> 00:41:15,308
His fiancée standing right over here.

551
00:41:15,388 --> 00:41:16,978
Fian…

552
00:41:34,078 --> 00:41:35,248
This isn't…

553
00:41:36,248 --> 00:41:37,958
a dream, right?

554
00:41:39,998 --> 00:41:40,958
You're…

555
00:41:42,168 --> 00:41:43,508
Gojin's fiancée?

556
00:41:46,178 --> 00:41:47,258
Yes.

557
00:41:50,598 --> 00:41:53,558
You really got engaged to Gojin?

558
00:41:54,268 --> 00:41:55,268
Pardon?

559
00:41:58,228 --> 00:41:59,228
Yes.

560
00:42:00,268 --> 00:42:01,108
When?

561
00:42:01,188 --> 00:42:02,568
A month ago…

562
00:42:04,188 --> 00:42:07,108
the two of us exchanged vows

563
00:42:08,158 --> 00:42:09,778
at his vacation house in Gangneung.

564
00:42:09,868 --> 00:42:10,818
A month ago?

565
00:42:16,908 --> 00:42:19,038
You know how close I am to Gojin, right?

566
00:42:19,998 --> 00:42:22,748
You're very close friends.

567
00:42:22,838 --> 00:42:26,468
No, we're not just close friends.

568
00:42:26,548 --> 00:42:29,888
He and I are like real brothers.

569
00:42:29,968 --> 00:42:34,428
But Gojin never told me anything
about exchanging vows.

570
00:42:34,518 --> 00:42:36,768
No, I've never heard him
mentioning you at all…

571
00:42:37,388 --> 00:42:38,308
I do.

572
00:42:38,808 --> 00:42:40,848
I'll go right after the special lecture

573
00:42:40,938 --> 00:42:43,398
and spend an amazing time
with my girlfriend. So don't you dare

574
00:42:43,768 --> 00:42:45,398
call me from the States.

575
00:42:47,278 --> 00:42:49,948
No way. He wasn't bluffing?

576
00:43:00,458 --> 00:43:01,288
Hello?

577
00:43:03,878 --> 00:43:04,878
Yes.

578
00:43:05,958 --> 00:43:07,798
Yes, okay. Bye.

579
00:43:24,648 --> 00:43:25,768
I fully understand.

580
00:43:27,318 --> 00:43:28,318
Pardon?

581
00:43:42,498 --> 00:43:44,838
There's more in the refrigerator.

582
00:43:45,588 --> 00:43:47,128
You're always full of surprises, Gojin.

583
00:43:48,048 --> 00:43:49,048
Sorry?

584
00:43:54,598 --> 00:43:55,678
Take a look at this.

585
00:43:57,218 --> 00:43:58,218
Is that…

586
00:43:59,218 --> 00:44:00,228
me?

587
00:44:00,518 --> 00:44:01,518
Yes, it is.

588
00:44:01,768 --> 00:44:04,098
We took it on your birthday
just a few days ago.

589
00:44:06,518 --> 00:44:10,108
This is a picture of us
from six years ago.

590
00:44:11,148 --> 00:44:12,238
At the time,

591
00:44:12,908 --> 00:44:15,698
we were practically living in the office

592
00:44:15,988 --> 00:44:17,528
building up Gotop.

593
00:44:19,038 --> 00:44:20,408
-I see.
-Do you remember?

594
00:44:23,368 --> 00:44:24,368
I'm…

595
00:44:26,288 --> 00:44:28,048
much better looking than you.

596
00:44:30,708 --> 00:44:32,088
You're still full of yourself.

597
00:44:34,718 --> 00:44:38,258
I was just stating a fact.

598
00:44:42,938 --> 00:44:46,808
You really don't remember my face?

599
00:44:50,898 --> 00:44:52,028
No, I don't.

600
00:45:10,458 --> 00:45:12,878
Something urgent came up at work,
so I'll head out first.

601
00:45:12,968 --> 00:45:14,718
I'll come back as soon as I finish up.

602
00:45:14,798 --> 00:45:16,088
Okay.

603
00:45:23,558 --> 00:45:26,688
Please take good care of Gojin.

604
00:45:28,398 --> 00:45:29,358
Okay.

605
00:45:39,778 --> 00:45:41,538
He believed me so easily.

606
00:45:49,498 --> 00:45:50,458
Hello?

607
00:45:50,538 --> 00:45:51,958
You dropped off dry cleaning?

608
00:45:52,378 --> 00:45:53,378
Yes.

609
00:45:58,428 --> 00:45:59,638
Thank you.

