00:46:10,228 --> 00:46:11,058
NEWS NOW
CEO NOH IN HIT-AND-RUN

613
00:46:11,148 --> 00:46:12,608
GOTOP CEO NOH GOJIN IN A HIT-AND-RUN

614
00:46:12,688 --> 00:46:15,528
The famous instructor Noh Gojin
was hit by a hit-and-run driver

615
00:46:15,688 --> 00:46:20,368
in front of his vacation home
in Gangneung this morning.

616
00:46:20,568 --> 00:46:23,618
Mr. Noh was found
by Ms. Lee, his secretary.

617
00:46:23,698 --> 00:46:25,198
He was unconscious when he was found…

618
00:46:25,288 --> 00:46:27,458
-Give us an update!
-Please tell us!

619
00:46:27,958 --> 00:46:29,628
MR. NOH, WE BELIEVE YOU'LL RETURN!
WE'LL PROTECT YOU

620
00:46:29,748 --> 00:46:30,918
LET'S PROTECT NOH GOJIN

621
00:46:40,718 --> 00:46:44,218
Is that true
that it wasn't just a hit-and-run?

622
00:46:44,308 --> 00:46:46,218
Did someone attempt to kill Mr. Noh?

623
00:46:46,308 --> 00:46:47,678
Was it motivated by revenge?

624
00:46:51,228 --> 00:46:53,108
The police are still investigating.

625
00:46:53,188 --> 00:46:56,488
I apologize, but I can't provide
any more information.

626
00:46:56,988 --> 00:46:58,028
Wait, sir!

627
00:46:58,108 --> 00:46:59,608
-Mr. Oh!
-Please tell us!

628
00:46:59,698 --> 00:47:00,858
-Please tell us!
-Mr. Oh!

629
00:47:03,948 --> 00:47:04,948
Please restrict access

630
00:47:05,078 --> 00:47:07,998
-and ask the police for assistance.
-Yes, sir.

631
00:47:08,658 --> 00:47:09,868
Mr. Oh.

632
00:47:10,038 --> 00:47:12,708
Please make sure Gangneung police
and the hospital keep quiet.

633
00:47:12,788 --> 00:47:14,538
Those are the only sources of information.

634
00:47:14,628 --> 00:47:16,088
-You're right!
-Gosh.

635
00:47:16,168 --> 00:47:17,758
I heard that…

636
00:47:26,058 --> 00:47:28,018
Mr. Oh, is it really true?

637
00:47:28,598 --> 00:47:31,098
The news only mentions
that it was a hit-and-run.

638
00:47:31,558 --> 00:47:34,018
Did someone really try to kill Mr. Noh?

639
00:47:34,938 --> 00:47:39,108
Who is this scumbag that did
such a terrible thing to our CEO?

640
00:47:39,188 --> 00:47:41,068
The police are still investigating.

641
00:47:42,738 --> 00:47:43,658
What in the world?

642
00:47:43,738 --> 00:47:47,158
It's not surprising. I'm sure
many people hold grudges against Mr. Noh.

643
00:47:47,238 --> 00:47:49,788
I knew he'd be destroyed
like this one day.

644
00:47:50,368 --> 00:47:51,578
Ouch! Hey--

645
00:47:55,248 --> 00:47:56,088
I'm sorry.

646
00:47:58,208 --> 00:48:00,718
The police requested our cooperation
for their investigation.

647
00:48:00,798 --> 00:48:03,928
They might ask you a few questions.

648
00:48:04,428 --> 00:48:05,848
I ask for your full cooperation.

649
00:48:06,428 --> 00:48:07,468
-Yes, sir.
-Yes, sir.

650
00:48:07,808 --> 00:48:09,728
It's going to be a bit hectic for a while.

651
00:48:09,808 --> 00:48:12,728
Please use the employee-only entrance.

652
00:48:13,848 --> 00:48:16,728
I have one more request.

653
00:48:17,318 --> 00:48:19,568
Please avoid reporters.

654
00:48:20,068 --> 00:48:24,488
An unnecessary comment could result
in misunderstanding and rumors

655
00:48:24,568 --> 00:48:28,238
that end up hindering Gotop Education.
So, please be extra mindful.

656
00:48:28,328 --> 00:48:29,658
-Yes, sir.
-Understood.

657
00:48:31,198 --> 00:48:32,328
Lastly,

658
00:48:33,288 --> 00:48:34,788
there's no need to be shaken up.

659
00:48:35,418 --> 00:48:36,788
You have nothing to worry about.

660
00:48:36,878 --> 00:48:40,458
Mr. Noh is fine and will return soon.

661
00:48:44,468 --> 00:48:45,468
Mr. Oh!

662
00:48:46,798 --> 00:48:47,848
Gosh.

663
00:48:48,808 --> 00:48:50,218
Is Mr. Noh all right?

664
00:48:50,308 --> 00:48:53,638
Yes, he is. His surgery went well,
and he's recovering fine too.

665
00:48:54,638 --> 00:48:58,938
Perhaps…
someone really hit him on purpose?

666
00:48:59,018 --> 00:49:00,228
We don't know yet.

667
00:49:00,318 --> 00:49:03,198
The police are investigating
with that possibility in mind.

668
00:49:03,278 --> 00:49:04,568
I see.

669
00:49:05,448 --> 00:49:09,578
Oh, I'll just need to postpone
his show schedule by one week, right?

670
00:49:09,658 --> 00:49:14,158
The producers keep calling the office.

671
00:49:14,538 --> 00:49:17,878
They're throwing a fuss
worried that their shows will be affected.

672
00:49:18,788 --> 00:49:21,588
Well then, I'll inform them.

673
00:49:23,418 --> 00:49:24,298
Ms. Ma.

674
00:49:25,968 --> 00:49:30,008
The doctor says he must rest still.

675
00:49:30,098 --> 00:49:34,058
I see. Then two weeks will suffice, right?

676
00:49:41,648 --> 00:49:42,528
Hello?

677
00:49:43,278 --> 00:49:44,898
Yes, okay.

678
00:49:45,858 --> 00:49:48,028
Let's give that some more thought.

679
00:50:04,258 --> 00:50:07,178
Noh is currently recovering
after emergency surgery.

680
00:50:07,258 --> 00:50:10,048
It has been revealed
he is not in critical condition.

681
00:50:10,388 --> 00:50:13,308
According to the police's initial report
from the scene of the accident,

682
00:50:13,388 --> 00:50:16,938
although there were
several surveillance cameras in the area,

683
00:50:17,018 --> 00:50:18,648
they were not working properly

684
00:50:18,728 --> 00:50:21,228
causing difficulties in finding evidence
for the hit-and-run driver…

685
00:50:23,148 --> 00:50:24,108
Hello?

686
00:50:24,608 --> 00:50:25,858
Mr. Oh is here.

687
00:50:26,358 --> 00:50:27,488
How is it?

688
00:50:27,818 --> 00:50:30,198
He is calm. But…

689
00:50:31,068 --> 00:50:33,618
I don't think it was just a hit-and-run.

690
00:50:34,738 --> 00:50:35,908
There's something more.

691
00:50:36,538 --> 00:50:38,538
Got it. Keep a close eye on him.

692
00:50:38,958 --> 00:50:40,708
And call me right away
if anything happens.

693
