FROM GOTOP EDUCATION CEO NOH GOJIN

694
00:50:51,968 --> 00:50:53,348
Noh Gojin!

695
00:50:56,638 --> 00:50:58,978
Who did such a great thing?

696
00:50:59,058 --> 00:51:01,308
WISH YOU HEALTHY BOWEL MOVEMENTS
FROM NOH GOJIN

697
00:51:35,388 --> 00:51:37,518
Darn it, why aren't you picking up?

698
00:51:59,498 --> 00:52:00,828
How may I help you?

699
00:52:00,908 --> 00:52:03,628
Is Ms. Baek Sooyeong
in Room 1210 here now?

700
00:52:04,668 --> 00:52:06,918
She just stepped out.

701
00:52:06,998 --> 00:52:07,998
Oh, is that right?

702
00:52:10,378 --> 00:52:12,128
Then could you please give this to her?

703
00:52:12,218 --> 00:52:13,678
Okay, we will.

704
00:52:13,758 --> 00:52:14,588
Thank you.

705
00:52:16,298 --> 00:52:17,388
Are you all right?

706
00:52:18,768 --> 00:52:21,688
-Yes.
-But you look so pale.

707
00:52:22,058 --> 00:52:23,348
Are you really all right?

708
00:52:24,558 --> 00:52:26,358
Yes, I'm fine.

709
00:53:12,108 --> 00:53:13,528
Hello? Dad?

710
00:53:14,778 --> 00:53:15,778
What are you doing?

711
00:53:16,528 --> 00:53:18,068
I… I'm at work.

712
00:53:19,368 --> 00:53:22,998
Is that right?
Isn't that the sound of waves I hear?

713
00:53:23,158 --> 00:53:24,458
Are you in Gangwon Province?

714
00:53:25,748 --> 00:53:30,298
It's the sound from a video
on my computer.

715
00:53:30,378 --> 00:53:33,128
I see. On your computer.

716
00:53:33,758 --> 00:53:35,928
I thought you were here.

717
00:53:36,468 --> 00:53:39,008
Is everything okay?

718
00:53:40,638 --> 00:53:42,348
Yes, it is.

719
00:53:43,888 --> 00:53:45,478
Nothing much is going on.

720
00:53:46,188 --> 00:53:47,098
Why do you ask?

721
00:53:47,188 --> 00:53:51,688
I just asked because…
I've been having bad dreams lately.

722
00:53:52,778 --> 00:53:55,398
That's good if everything is okay.

723
00:53:57,778 --> 00:53:59,618
Are you crying?

724
00:53:59,698 --> 00:54:02,158
No… Why would I cry?

725
00:54:05,658 --> 00:54:07,328
It sounded like you were crying.

726
00:54:07,918 --> 00:54:12,798
By the way,
did your boss get into a car accident?

727
00:54:13,958 --> 00:54:15,378
How did you know, Dad?

728
00:54:15,758 --> 00:54:17,338
I saw it on TV.

729
00:54:17,928 --> 00:54:18,888
I see.

730
00:54:19,838 --> 00:54:22,508
Maybe that's why I had bad dreams.

731
00:54:24,558 --> 00:54:25,558
Take good care of him.

732
00:54:27,138 --> 00:54:28,268
Okay.

733
00:54:29,398 --> 00:54:31,268
I'll take good care of him.

734
00:54:32,568 --> 00:54:35,528
The police in charge restricted access
to Mr. Noh Gojin's vacation house

735
00:54:35,608 --> 00:54:37,608
and are searching for witnesses…

736
00:54:37,698 --> 00:54:40,068
My accident is being reported on the news.

737
00:54:40,868 --> 00:54:43,908
Considering the fact the accident happened
in front of Noh's vacation house,

738
00:54:43,988 --> 00:54:45,618
they're keeping all possibilities open

739
00:54:45,698 --> 00:54:49,498
and will focus all their efforts
on finding a suspect.

740
00:54:49,578 --> 00:54:50,828
I kept thinking about it.

741
00:54:51,878 --> 00:54:54,088
I couldn't eat or sleep.

742
00:54:55,708 --> 00:54:57,758
I kept thinking over and over again

743
00:54:59,088 --> 00:55:00,758
trying to figure out
why you're doing this.

744
00:55:05,598 --> 00:55:07,228
Are you doing this on purpose?

745
00:55:08,138 --> 00:55:10,188
You're pretending
not to know me on purpose, right?

746
00:55:14,478 --> 00:55:15,728
Or is it revenge?

747
00:55:17,068 --> 00:55:20,818
Are you still upset with me
that you're getting revenge like this?

748
00:55:21,068 --> 00:55:23,738
But how can you be so cruel
and ignore me like this--

749
00:55:23,828 --> 00:55:24,698
Excuse me.

750
00:55:26,868 --> 00:55:28,618
You were like this last time too.

751
00:55:30,998 --> 00:55:31,878
Who are you?

752
00:55:32,788 --> 00:55:33,748
What's wrong with you?

753
00:55:34,838 --> 00:55:36,208
I'm sorry,

754
00:55:37,758 --> 00:55:39,418
but I have amnesia.

755
00:55:40,588 --> 00:55:42,338
So I can't remember anything.

756
00:55:43,798 --> 00:55:45,178
Do you know me?

757
00:55:50,058 --> 00:55:52,018
Amnesia?

758
00:55:55,938 --> 00:55:57,818
What the heck are you talking…

759
00:55:59,568 --> 00:56:00,608
Mr. Noh.

760
00:56:06,988 --> 00:56:09,748
I suppose he knows me very well too.

761
00:56:10,658 --> 00:56:12,668
LOBBY

762
00:56:22,378 --> 00:56:24,298
He has amnesia?

763
00:56:44,358 --> 00:56:47,528
It's me. Can you find
some information on a patient?

764
00:56:48,868 --> 00:56:50,788
He's in Room 1202
at Gangneung Medical Center.

765
00:56:51,698 --> 00:56:52,908
His name is Noh Gojin.

766
00:56:57,748 --> 00:56:58,918
LAWYER BAE BYUNHO

767
00:56:58,998 --> 00:57:01,418
I'm Bae Byunho, a lawyer.
You remember me, don't you?

768
00:57:02,298 --> 00:57:03,418
How did this happen--

769
00:57:04,048 --> 00:57:05,218
Gosh, I'm so sorry.

770
00:57:05,298 --> 00:57:07,428
I just got a call from Mr. Oh.

771
00:57:07,508 --> 00:57:10,138
How can you have amnesia?
It's like a bolt from the blue!

772
00:57:10,218 --> 00:57:13,268
My heart is still pounding so hard
from the shock.

773
00:57:13,348 --> 00:57:14,478
I'm here…

774
00:57:17,558 --> 00:57:18,568
Please say hello.

775
00:57:19,608 --> 00:57:20,938
That's my fiancée.

776
00:57:21,528 --> 00:57:22,398
Fiancée?

777
00:57:22,488 --> 00:57:23,358
Who?

778
00:57:25,278 --> 00:57:27,068
This person right here.

779
00:57:29,908 --> 00:57:30,988
Who?

780
00:57:31,658 --> 00:57:32,618
Don't you know?

781
00:57:33,748 --> 00:57:35,078
She's my secretary.

782
00:57:35,458 --> 00:57:36,288
Who?

783
00:57:47,218 --> 00:57:49,508
You're Mr. Noh's fiancée?

784
00:57:50,718 --> 00:57:51,558
Yes.

785
00:57:51,638 --> 00:57:54,768
Anything you say can and will be used
against you in a court of law.

786
00:57:54,888 --> 00:57:56,228
-Pardon?
-It's odd.

787
00:57:56,308 --> 00:57:57,938
Mr. Noh has amnesia,

788
00:57:58,018 --> 00:57:59,858
and suddenly,
you're saying you're his fiancée.

789
00:57:59,938 --> 00:58:02,648
Honestly, I can't help but doubt you.

790
00:58:02,728 --> 00:58:06,068
You know that Mr. Noh's stalker
pretended to be his fiancée before, right?

791
00:58:07,108 --> 00:58:08,068
Fine.

792
00:58:10,778 --> 00:58:13,828
Anything you say can and will be used
against you in a court of law.

793
00:58:14,788 --> 00:58:16,288
Are you really Mr. Noh's fiancée?

794
00:58:24,128 --> 00:58:25,258
She is.

795
00:58:26,588 --> 00:58:28,008
Mr. Oh.

796
00:58:28,088 --> 00:58:29,088
Hello, sir.

797
00:58:29,178 --> 00:58:30,088
Ms. Lee…

798
00:58:30,968 --> 00:58:32,558
is Mr. Noh's fiancée.

799
00:58:33,178 --> 00:58:34,058
Pardon?

800
00:58:34,138 --> 00:58:36,348
Mr. Noh is especially sensitive
about this issue

801
00:58:36,428 --> 00:58:39,848
because he's harassed
by all sorts of rumors.

802
00:58:40,768 --> 00:58:41,858
So he was careful about it.

803
00:58:43,478 --> 00:58:45,028
Oh, I see.

804
00:58:45,608 --> 00:58:47,528
But why did you come here?

