00:58:48,318 --> 00:58:50,818
I asked you to come to my office.

806
00:58:50,908 --> 00:58:53,828
I thought I should pay him a visit.

807
00:58:53,908 --> 00:58:58,788
Don't you know all too well
that people are watching

808
00:58:59,958 --> 00:59:01,328
Mr. Noh's every movement?

809
00:59:01,918 --> 00:59:02,748
I'm sorry, sir.

810
00:59:02,838 --> 00:59:04,298
Please be careful.

811
00:59:06,048 --> 00:59:07,048
And…

812
00:59:08,218 --> 00:59:09,048
please apologize.

813
00:59:10,968 --> 00:59:11,968
I'm sorry.

814
00:59:13,598 --> 00:59:14,598
Okay.

815
00:59:15,848 --> 00:59:17,428
Well, I understand clearly now.

816
00:59:18,058 --> 00:59:20,848
Ma'am, please take care.

817
00:59:21,598 --> 00:59:23,438
-Bye, sir.
-Thank you. I'll give you a call.

818
00:59:24,398 --> 00:59:25,358
Is it going down?

819
