ENDOSCOPE, FAMILY REST AREA

820
00:59:33,568 --> 00:59:34,778
When did you get here?

821
00:59:35,618 --> 00:59:36,618
Just now.

822
00:59:38,288 --> 00:59:40,248
How is Gojin? Is everything okay?

823
00:59:40,958 --> 00:59:41,788
Yes.

824
00:59:42,458 --> 00:59:44,128
That's good. Let's go inside.

825
00:59:44,668 --> 00:59:47,668
Wait, I…

826
00:59:48,168 --> 00:59:50,548
Thank you for your help earlier.

827
00:59:52,048 --> 00:59:54,138
I just told the truth.

828
00:59:56,928 --> 00:59:59,978
But what about you?

829
01:00:02,938 --> 01:00:06,438
Do I suspect you
to be pretending to be his fiancée?

830
01:00:10,028 --> 01:00:12,028
-It doesn't matter.
-What?

831
01:00:12,108 --> 01:00:15,408
Whether you're really his fiancée or not,

832
01:00:15,488 --> 01:00:16,908
it doesn't matter to me.

833
01:00:17,488 --> 01:00:18,908
That's not what's important.

834
01:00:19,868 --> 01:00:21,158
What's important is

835
01:00:21,248 --> 01:00:24,708
the fact that you're by Gojin's side.

836
01:00:25,328 --> 01:00:27,668
Just like the day he got hit by the car.

837
01:00:29,918 --> 01:00:32,218
If you weren't there that day,

838
01:00:33,128 --> 01:00:34,178
Gojin would've…

839
01:00:37,468 --> 01:00:39,058
died, right?

840
01:00:42,098 --> 01:00:43,978
Just thinking about it makes me shudder.

841
01:00:46,018 --> 01:00:47,058
Thank you, Ms. Lee.

842
01:00:49,068 --> 01:00:51,858
Gosh, I called you Ms. Lee again.

843
01:00:52,648 --> 01:00:53,488
Ma'am.

844
01:00:54,818 --> 01:00:57,368
I should call you that now, right?

845
01:00:58,028 --> 01:00:59,408
No, it's okay.

846
01:00:59,788 --> 01:01:02,078
Thank you, ma'am.

